												<span>Servette Music SA</span>
										</li>
										<li class="list-inline-item">
												<span>&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Rue de la Servette 92</span>
										</li>
										<li class="list-inline-item">
												<span>&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;CH - 1202 Genève</span>
										</li>
										<li class="list-inline-item">
												<span>&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;CHE- 103.215.282 TVA</span>
										</li>

										<li class="list-inline-item">
												<span class="o_force_ltr">&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Tél Mag. +41 22 733 70 73</span>
